description:
Returns the value constrained to the range defined by the minimum and maximum values.   <pre>
 var value:Number = 5;
 var min:Number = 0;
 var max:Number = 10;
 trace(clamp(value, min, max)); // 5
 value = -5;
 trace(clamp(value, min, max)); // 0
 value = 15;
 trace(clamp(value, min, max)); // 10
 </pre>
